  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">CPLF- Mriya</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IFC&apos;&apos;s financing will support resource and energy efficiency improvements at the sugar plants. The implementation of the project will achieve significant reductions in energy consumption, water use and CO2 emissions. As a result, Mriya will realize direct economic benefits and enhance its competitiveness.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Project (CPLF-Mryia) involves providing a long-term financing to Mriya Agro Holding Public Limited (Mriya or the Company), a leading Ukrainian primary agricultural producer with a proven track record of growing wheat, barley, sugar beet, rapeseed, potatoes, and other crops. The long-term loan will provide financing to improve the operational processes and resource efficiencies at the sugar plant companies.</narrative>
  </description>
